videos.description: Warriors coach Steve Kerr admits that halfway through the third quarter they fell apart and says that DeMarcus Cousins' injury is "significant."

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Presser (Kerr on Warriors’ loss: ‘We stopped playing’) 2019/4/15

videos.headline: Kerr on Warriors' loss: 'We stopped playing'

videos.description: After the Clippers come back from a 31-point deficit to beat the Warriors in Game 2, Doc Rivers tells the media they have bigger goals in sight.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Press Conference (Rivers: We didn’t come here to win one game) 2019/4/16

videos.headline: Rivers: We didn't come here to win one game

videos.description: Landry Shamet tells Shelley's Smith that he and the Clippers are familiar with facing adversity and Game 2 at Oracle was no different.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (Shamet on Clips’ comeback: ‘We’ve been there before') 2019/4/15

videos.headline: Shamet on Clips' comeback: 'We've been there before'

videos.description: Lou Williams and Montrezl Harrell discuss being huge underdogs vs. the Warriors, then Williams jokes about all the questions they were asked.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Presser (Williams: ‘You get a lot more questions when you win’) 2019/04/15

videos.headline: Williams: 'You get a lot more questions when you win'

videos.description: After the Clippers' historic comeback win vs. the Warriors, Patrick Beverley says he can't help if people are "irritated" by him and talks about defending Kevin Durant.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (Beverley: ‘KD’s not an easy cover, but it’s fun out there’) 2019/4/15

videos.headline: Beverley: 'KD's not an easy cover, but it's fun out there'

videos.description: Nick Friedell says the Warriors' locker room is in "stunned silence" after blowing a 31-point lead and watching DeMarcus Cousins go down with an injury in Game 2.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (Friedell: Warriors ‘aura of invincibility’ broken) 2019/4/15 ESHEET SC

videos.headline: Friedell: Warriors 'aura of invincibility' broken
